JUNE, I AM SO SORRY.

08:42.189 --> 08:44.191
CHLOE SAID SHE TOLD YOU

08:42.189 --> 08:44.191
I WAS HER DAD.

08:44.232 --> 08:45.566
I MEAN, I ADMIT AT FIRST,

08:45.608 --> 08:46.860
THE AGE DIFFERENCE

08:45.608 --> 08:46.860
WAS A BIT... STRANGE,

08:46.901 --> 08:49.154
BUT SHE SAID WE WERE REALLY

08:46.901 --> 08:49.154
GONNA GET ALONG, AND WE DID.

08:49.196 --> 08:51.656
YEAH, 'CAUSE, JUNE,

08:49.196 --> 08:51.656
INTERNALLY, YOU'RE, LIKE, 50.

08:51.698 --> 08:53.616
THIS ONE IS

08:51.698 --> 08:53.616
SUCH A LITTLE RASCAL.

